div.p:
Frequent Sailings from ALEXANDRIA to LIVERPOOL, also Regular Services
                            from LIVERPOOL to ALEXANDRIA and to ALGERIA, MALTA, LEVANT, BLACK SEA,
                            and other Mediterranean Ports.

The annnal children's festival will be held at the Institute on New
                            Year's Day. The pro-gramme is as follows : 2 p.m, sports ; 5 p.m., tea ;
                            6 p.m., cinematograph ; 8 p.m., concert ; 10 p.m., dance.
